LINUX - Tomcat

#Kill "tomcatOreilly"
	- Be sure to call out in chat that you about to Kill OPS (tomcat)
	- This command restarts OPS and some behind the scene processors
sudo su -c "/usr/local/oreilly/bin/stopPointOfSale.sh; /usr/local/oreilly/bin/stopOreillyTomcat.sh"

#Kill Enactor/Stop enactor Tomcat/Restart enactor tomcat
	- Stops entire Enactor including CCT (bigger than OreillyTomcat)
	- sudo /usr/local/oreilly/bin/stopEnactorTomcat.sh


